{"title":"党中央公报振奋人心","authors":["喻晓"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":8,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"党中央公报振奋人心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军工程兵某部　喻晓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长空电波播公报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党中央发出战斗号召；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山笑水笑人欢笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢呼的声浪似海潮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公报字字金光闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想红旗飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"句句说到咱心坎里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的指示记得牢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公报好似进军号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七亿人民斗志高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢干敢闯敢革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大风大浪逞英豪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公报如同战鼓响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的风雷震四方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛鬼蛇神齐清扫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新世界我们来创造！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公报就像千钧棒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把帝、修、反的丧钟敲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁敢碰我们铁打的江山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全部、干净把它消灭掉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党中央公报震人心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激动的话儿涌出口："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟着领袖毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终生革命不动摇！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}